{"tid":1334732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我有朋友係某傳媒娛樂版記者，但最近佢自告奮勇轉Team上前線，轉職做戰地記者","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T10:12:18.000Z","uid":76632,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"625f8295965bd8011467a86c6437371ec5eeee59","tid":1334732,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"我朋友本身係娛樂記者（佢主要跟日韓流行文化，唔係狗仔隊），我平時係娛樂台開Post覆Post都靠佢提供圖片及情報支援，而佢有時都會借我AC上來娛樂台收風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但近期佢公司前線記者人手不足，所以佢決定暫時轉職做戰地記者，上最前線用鏡頭守護真相同埋保衛香港嘅新聞自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話想影低差佬嘅惡行，同埋記錄抗爭者團結嘅時刻，佢希望7月21可以見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n佢張記者證我唔會貼上來，廢事被Mon Post狗起底，到時又記我朋友老母又用警棍打我朋友。信不信柔理（由你）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全文總結，7月21，請支持我老友同香港人，為自由而戰！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0d48631298f5daae0732d23bf26713ea5e29c360","tid":1334732,"uid":30163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"da72fdb459fb93bb2aae494ee6fa7b0ddc3b5735","tid":1334732,"uid":67049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"總之就全民皆兵 咩都唔撚理啦<br />\n721出左黎支持香港人就得<br />\n我地香港人最撚硬頸 係唔撚會認輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0759bb3a2cc46fe6c9bd25f7e07441669d7cd39","tid":1334732,"uid":62929,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢全民皆兵　<br />\n中學生都上前線啦<br />\n唔使借D二呃正評喇<br />\n推下7.21啲Post好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dfa3b3155f6abc72d70e3495f89d157a320f65","tid":1334732,"uid":76632,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da72fdb459fb93bb2aae494ee6fa7b0ddc3b5735","tid":1334732,"uid":67049,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"總之就全民皆兵 咩都唔撚理啦<br />\n721出左黎支持香港人就得<br />\n我地香港人最撚硬頸 係唔撚會認輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"由於記者身份，我朋友係唔會出手明幫抗爭者，但佢會同大家一樣企起最前線，為香港而戰。"},{"pid":"01dbe21ff6460c53478d1cf86e973a336a75f841","tid":1334732,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"Last Push.<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"d94654ed1ae5d8cc9b060dea1eae8c36e54d842e","tid":1334732,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac0a0d12e7a77eb47434cc1d1ea9c933e54bfea","tid":1334732,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"收到風 愚樂台好多會員都係撈韓娛圈"},{"pid":"329c6089ec2102cfc86e9ed25a0a121b402d4d95","tid":1334732,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac0a0d12e7a77eb47434cc1d1ea9c933e54bfea","tid":1334732,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"收到風 愚樂台好多會員都係撈韓娛圈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VdSEgb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VdSEgb.gif&h=3f2e7d8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"605f91d3ec35788c068329cfd0d05f739fe13df4","tid":1334732,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"